button.description:
## Description développeur
Le composant `button` est l'élément interactif fondamental du Design System, responsable de l'invocation d'actions utilisateur. Il supporte trois tailles (sm, md, lg) avec scaling proportionnel du padding, font-size et iconSize, ainsi que des variantes sémantiques (primary, secondary, tertiary, destructive). Le composant gère nativement tous les états critiques (default, hover, active, focus avec ring WCAG AA, disabled, loading) via des variables CSS et transitions fluides. Il intègre une gestion pixel-perfect du gap icon-texte, du minHeight pour respecter les hit-targets de 44×44px minimum, et applique strictement la hiérarchie typographique avec font-weight semibold et line-height normal.

## Do & Don't

✅ **Do**
- Utiliser la taille `md` par défaut pour les actions primaires ; réserver `sm` aux contextes compacts (dense tables, toolbars) et `lg` aux CTAs critiques
- Toujours fournir un `aria-label` explicite si l'icône seule remplace le texte ; inclure des icônes 16×20×24px selon la taille
- Appliquer `disabled` plutôt que désactiver via CSS ; le navigateur gère nativement le focus et les événements
- Tester systématiquement le focus visible (2px ring primaire) au clavier ; respecter l'ordre tabulation logique
- Gérer les états de loading avec un spinner aligné et une classe aria-busy pour l'accessibilité vocale

❌ **Don't**
- Ajouter des ombres drop-shadow ou effets visuels non définis dans les tokens (zero tolerance pour le styling ad-hoc)
- Combiner des variantes incompatibles (ex: `primary` + `outline` simultanément sans spec)
- Ignorer la contrainte minHeight : un button `sm` doit toujours mesurer min 32px, `md` 40px, `lg` 48px
- Utiliser des classes Tailwind de couleur (bg-blue-500, text-white) : injecter uniquement via CSS variables
- Placer du contenu complexe (formulaires, dropdowns) à l'intérieur sans wrapper sémantique dédié

## 💻 Code interactif (Live Editor)

```jsx
const css = `
  /* Reset et base */
  .ds-button {
    font-family: var(--component-button-fontFamily, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif);
    font-weight: var(--component-button-fontWeight, 600);
    border-radius: var(--component-button-radius, 6px);
    border-width: var(--component-button-borderWidth, 1px);
    border-style: solid;
    transition: var(--component-button-transition, all 150ms ease-in-out);
    cursor: pointer;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    white-space: nowrap;
    user-select: none;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Taille sm */
  .ds-button-sm {
    padding: var(--component-button-size-sm-paddingY, 4px) var(--component-button-size-sm-paddingX, 8px);
    font-size: var(--component-button-size-sm-fontSize, 14px);
    line-height: var(--component-button-size-sm-lineHeight, 1.5);
    gap: var(--component-button-size-sm-gap, 4px);
    min-height: var(--component-button-size-sm-minHeight, 32px);
  }
  .ds-button-sm svg {
    width: var(--component-button-size-sm-iconSize, 16px);
    height: var(--component-button-size-sm-iconSize, 16px);
  }

  /* Taille md */
  .ds-button-md {
    padding: var(--component-button-size-md-paddingY, 8px) var(--component-button-size-md-paddingX, 16px);
    font-size: var(--component-button-size-md-fontSize, 14px);
    line-height: var(--component-button-size-md-lineHeight, 1.5);
    gap: var(--component-button-size-md-gap, 8px);
    min-height: var(--component-button-size-md-minHeight, 40px);
  }
  .ds-button-md svg {
    width: var(--component-button-size-md-iconSize, 20px);
    height: var(--component-button-size-md-iconSize, 20px);
  }

  /* Taille lg */
  .ds-button-lg {
    padding: var(--component-button-size-lg-paddingY, 8px) var(--component-button-size-lg-paddingX, 24px);
    font-size: var(--component-button-size-lg-fontSize, 16px);
    line-height: var(--component-button-size-lg-lineHeight, 1.5);
    gap: var(--component-button-size-lg-gap, 8px);
    min-height: var(--component-button-size-lg-minHeight, 48px);
  }
  .ds-button-lg svg {
    width: var(--component-button-size-lg-iconSize, 24px);
    height: var(--component-button-size-lg-iconSize, 24px);
  }

  /* Variante: Primary */
  .ds-button-primary {
    background-color: var(--semantic-color-action-primary-bg-default, #0066cc);
    color: var(--semantic-color-action-primary-text-default, #ffffff);
    border-color: var(--semantic-color-action-primary-border-default, #0066cc);
  }
  .ds-button-primary:hover:not(:disabled) {
    background-color: var(--semantic-color-action-primary-bg-hover, #0052a3);
    border-color: var(--semantic-color-action-primary-border-hover, #0052a3);
  }
  .ds-button-primary:active:not(:disabled) {
    background-color: var(--semantic-color-action-primary-bg-active, #003d7a);
    border-color: var(--semantic-color-action-primary-border-active, #003d7a);
  }

  /* Variante: Secondary */
  .ds-button-secondary {
    background-color: var(--semantic-color-action-secondary-bg-default, #f0f0f0);
    color: var(--semantic-color-action-secondary-text-default, #333333);
    border-color: var(--semantic-color-action-secondary-border-default, #d0d0d0);
  }
  .ds-button-secondary:hover:not(:disabled) {
    background-color: var(--semantic-color-action-secondary-bg-hover, #e0e0e0);
    border-color: var(--semantic-color-action-secondary-border-hover, #b0b0b0);
  }
  .ds-button-secondary:active:not(:disabled) {
    background-color: var(--semantic-color-action-secondary-bg-active, #d0d0d0);
    border-color: var(--semantic-color-action-secondary-border-active, #999999);
  }

  /* Variante: Tertiary (outline) */
  .ds-button-tertiary {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--semantic-color-action-tertiary-text-default, #0066cc);
    border-color: var(--semantic-color-action-tertiary-border-default, #0066cc);
  }
  .ds-button-tertiary:hover:not(:disabled) {
    background-color: var(--semantic-color-action-tertiary-bg-hover, #f0f7ff);
    border-color: var(--semantic-color-action-tertiary-border-hover, #0052a3);
    color: var(--semantic-color-action-tertiary-text-hover, #0052a3);
  }
  .ds-button-tertiary:active:not(:disabled) {
    background-color: var(--semantic-color-action-tertiary-bg-active, #e0efff);
    border-color: var(--semantic-color-action-tertiary-border-active, #003d7a);
    color: var(--semantic-color-action-tertiary-text-active, #003d7a);
  }

  /* Variante: Destructive */
  .ds-button-destructive {
    background-color: var(--semantic-color-action-destructive-bg-default, #cc0000);
    color: var(--semantic-color-action-destructive-text-default, #ffffff);
    border-color: var(--semantic-color-action-destructive-border-default, #cc0000);
  }
  .ds-button-destructive:hover:not(:disabled) {
    background-color: var(--semantic-color-action-destructive-bg-hover, #990000);
    border-color: var(--semantic-color-action-destructive-border-hover, #990000);
  }
  .ds-button-destructive:active:not(:disabled) {
    background-color: var(--semantic-color-action-destructive-bg-active, #660000);
    border-color: var(--semantic-color-action-destructive-border-active, #660000);
  }

  /* État disabled */
  .ds-button:disabled {
    opacity: 0.6;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }
  .ds-button:disabled:hover {
    background-color: inherit;
    border-color: inherit;
    color: inherit;
  }

  /* Focus ring (WCAG 2.2 AA) */
  .ds-button:focus-visible {
    outline: none;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 var(--component-button-focus-ringWidth, 2px) var(--component-button-focus-ringColor, #0066cc),
                0 0 0 calc(var(--component-button-focus-ringWidth, 2px) + var(--component-button-focus-ringOffset, 2px)) transparent;
  }

  /* État loading */
  .ds-button.is-loading {
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .ds-button.is-loading [data-slot="spinner"] {
    animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
  }
  @keyframes spin {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }
`;

const Button = ({ variant = 'primary', size = 'md', disabled = false, loading = false, icon = null, children, ...props }) => {
  const sizeClass = `ds-button-${size}`;
  const variantClass = `ds-button-${variant}`;
  const loadingClass = loading ? 'is-loading' : '';

  return (
    <button 
      className={`ds-button ${sizeClass} ${variantClass} ${loadingClass}`}
      disabled={disabled || loading}
      aria-busy={loading}
      {...props}
    >
      {loading && (
        <svg data-slot="spinner" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="2">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" opacity="0.25" />
          <path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 1 10 10" strokeLinecap="round" />
        </svg>
      )}
      {icon && !loading && <span data-slot="icon">{icon}</span>}
      {children && <span>{children}</span>}
    </button>
  );
};

const IconPlus = () => (
  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="2" strokeLinecap="round">
    <line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19" />
    <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12" />
  </svg>
);

const IconCheck = () => (
  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="2" strokeLinecap="round">
    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" />
  </svg>
);

const Showcase = () => {
  const [loadingStates, setLoadingStates] = React.useState({});

  const toggleLoading = (id) => {
    setLoadingStates(prev => ({
      ...prev,
      [id]: !prev[id]
    }));
  };

  return (
    <div className="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 space-y-8 bg-white">
      <style>{css}</style>

      {/* Variantes par taille */}
      <section>
        <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Variantes et Tailles</h2>
        <div className="space-y-6">
          {['sm', 'md', 'lg'].map(size => (
            <div key={size} className="flex gap-3 items-center flex-wrap">
              <span className="min-w-12 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 uppercase">{size}</span>
              <Button size={size} variant="primary">Primary</Button>
              <Button size={size} variant="secondary">Secondary</Button>
              <Button size={size} variant="tertiary">Tertiary</Button>
              <Button size={size} variant="destructive">Delete</Button>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Avec icônes */}
      <section>
        <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Avec Icônes</h2>
        <div className="flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <Button size="md" variant="primary" icon={<IconPlus />}>Create</Button>
          <Button size="md" variant="secondary" icon={<IconCheck />}>Validate</Button>
          <Button size="md" variant="tertiary" icon={<IconPlus />} />
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* États */}
      <section>
        <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">États</h2>
        <div className="flex gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <Button variant="primary">Default</Button>
          <Button variant="primary" disabled>Disabled</Button>
          <Button 
            variant="primary" 
            loading={loadingStates.main}
            onClick={() => toggleLoading('main')}
          >
            {loadingStates.main ? 'Loading...' : 'Click to load'}
          </Button>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* États loading par taille */}
      <section>
        <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Loading States</h2>
        <div className="space-y-4">
          {['sm', 'md', 'lg'].map(size => (
            <Button 
              key={`loading-${size}`}
              size={size} 
              variant="primary"
              loading={loadingStates[`load-${size}`]}
              onClick={() => toggleLoading(`load-${size}`)}
            >
              {loadingStates[`load-${size}`] ? 'Processing' : `Load ${size}`}
            </Button>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Accessibilité */}
      <section>
        <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Accessibilité (Tab pour focus-visible)</h2>
